7971.title: The Long Arm of the Godfather
7971.description: A "Mustache Pete" Mafia boss (Celi) seeks bloody retribution when is he double-crossed by a treacherous low-level hood (Lawrence). Watch for the sumptuous Italian bambina Erica Blanc!

8005.title: Revolver
8005.description: After violent criminals kidnap the wife of a tough prison warden and demand the release of an inmate, but the warden strikes back with a hostage of his own!

8056.title: The Cynic, the Rat & the Fist
8056.description: In one of best Italian crime thrillers of 70s, a cunning cop (Maurizio Merli) sees an opportunity to take the syndicate down when street warfare breaks out between a young ganster and a sadistic crime boss!

54901.title: Modus Operandi
54901.description: This shockingly violent 70s grindhouse throwback tells the tale of a CIA specialist who is called to find sensitive tapes stolen from the president.

230999.title: MST3K - Code Name: Diamond Head
230999.description: Counterintelligence takes on a new meaning in this barely coherent tale of Hawaiian espionage that takes place on movie sets meant to look like Hawaii.

275223.title: Ten Violent Women
275223.description: Tired of their life as miners, a group of women rob a jewelry store, but run into trouble after they're unable to sell the stolen jewels.

279408.title: Hell's Angels '69
279408.description: In one of the wildest robbery plots ever conceived, two wealthy brothers play a deadly game by infiltrating the ranks of the Hell's Angels.

289779.title: 5th Street
289779.description: A husband in inner-city Los Angeles is determined to track down the gang responsible for murdering his wife in this gritty action thriller.

302505.title: The Substitute
302505.description: Undercover as a substitute teacher, an ex-marine cleans up the crime-infested school when he discovers a gang tormenting students and staff.

302793.title: Caught In The Crossfire
302793.description: Two detectives investigating a gang-related crime find themselves targeted by both gang members and crooked cops.

307203.title: Blood Out
307203.description: Having assumed an undercover identity as a gangster to solve his brother's murder, a sheriff finds himself more in character than he anticipated.

312169.title: Brannigan
312169.description: A former police detective from Chicago is sent to England to retrieve an American racketeer. But the criminal is kidnapped before he arrives.

312178.title: Foxy Brown
312178.description: After her brother betrays her, a woman goes undercover as a prostitute in order to find the gangsters who killed her boyfriend — and get revenge.

314511.title: 22 Bullets
314511.description: Having been left for dead with 22 bullets in his body after being shot by a former childhood friend, a retired mobster sets out to get his revenge.

317189.title: Fatal Beauty
317189.description: When a tainted drug shipment hits the streets of L.A., a witty narcotics cop goes undercover to investigate in this fast-paced romantic comedy.

354260.title: Gone in 60 Seconds
354260.description: Buckle-up as Eleanor, the fast and furious Ford Fastback Mustang, takes you on a full-throttle ride you'll never forget. The Assignment: To steal 48 muscle and exotic cars! The Challenge: Avoid getting caught!

360635.title: Top Coat Cash
360635.description: After losing a major fight, a professional MMA fighter returns home from Vegas, where he reunites with various individuals from his past - including a father/son duo who recruit him to engage in their daring bank heists.

361082.title: Road to Juarez
361082.description: An American ex-con with Mexican underworld ties ensnares a pair of young misfits into a dangerous heist in Mexico. Inspired by true events.

367659.title: Asian Schoolgirls
367659.description: A group of girls seek murderous revenge on a Los Angeles crime gang after they are kidnapped and abused, causing their friend to commit suicide.

367803.title: Ready 2 Die
367803.description: After stealing a bag of cash, a group of bank robbers must fend off gangs and crooked cops alike as they strive to keep their loot and stay alive.

376058.title: Mob Rules
376058.description: Two criminals travel across the country to locate their former partner in order to retrieve the money they're owed from a failed heist years earlier.

386218.title: A Gangland Love Story
386218.description: When the sister of a crime lord falls in love with a man from a rival gang, they steal a car to run away but its cargo makes them a bigger target.

386243.title: Copaholic
386243.description: Pressure mounts between two undercover cops while they track down a murderer, as corruption makes it hard for them to trust anyone, even each other.

407870.title: Underground P.D.
407870.description: An elite team of detectives assigned to capture the city's most violent felons gets unwanted help from a murderer that is apprehending them first.

407899.title: Hostile Takedown
407899.description: Nine years after leaving the force, Alex is forced back on the job when a madman with connections to his slain former partner takes over a mall.

416204.title: A Special Lady
416204.description: Na Hyun-jing, a charismatic female boss who turned a crime organization into a legal business enterprise, is planning to retire and start a new life. However, her decision to break clean from the past is met with obstacles from inside and out. In addition, Dae-shik, a vindictive prosecutor who was coerced by Hyun-jung to help build up the gang’s business, plots a revenge. When the existence of Hyun-jung’s son is revealed, he instantly becomes the target of all her enemies. Will she be able to save her son and leave the underworld?

436413.title: Turf War
436413.description: A detective chasing down rogue cops sets out to prove that his sergeant has been framing area murders on a pair of motorcycle gang members.

449105.title: Narx
449105.description: Based on a true story, an undercover cop risks his life to fight police corruption while trying to take down New York's biggest drug kingpin.

449366.title: Extraordinary Mission
449366.description: An undercover police officer in China becomes embroiled in a fierce attempt to take down a hostile drug trafficking syndicate from the inside.

449528.title: The Killing Zone
449528.description: A convicted man is recruited from the chain gang he’s been sentenced to in order to help capture a Mexican drug lord in a ruthless chase.

451340.title: Machine
451340.description: A former mercenary turned criminal is tasked with killing three witnesses testifying against his new boss, while the top lieutenant keeps him on task.

452676.title: Dark Meridian
452676.description: A corrupt New Orleans detective gets caught up in a fight between two criminal gangs and must find a killer on the run before he strikes again.

454189.title: The Shop
454189.description: Two friends running an auto repair must dodge rough locals, rogue cops, and diamond hunters when one inherits a 1966 Mustang full of stashed diamonds.

454199.title: King of the Game
454199.description: A man trying to leave the crime game gets drawn in further when he decides to rescue a woman from prostitution and a boss marks him for murder.

456638.title: Mundo: From Altar Boy to Hitman
456638.description: Based on a true story, Ramon “Mundo” Mendoza follows a life of gang violence in and outside of prison, until he falls in love and finds religion.

456912.title: Scarred City
456912.description: A young cop is trained to be a ruthless killer as part of a police hit squad. But when he has second thoughts, he'll have to fight his own.

457471.title: Send No Flowers
457471.description: When her crime boss father is murdered, a woman decides to take over the family business, but soon learns the mafia is the ultimate men’s club.

458202.title: They Call Me Jeeg
458202.description: When a crook from a poor Italian town falls into the Tiber River and gains special powers, he plans to be a super-criminal, until he falls in love.

458480.title: Big Bag of $
458480.description: Five desperate people clash over an unclaimed bag of money, and they're willing to do the unthinkable to come out holding the cash.

458481.title: Gangster Party
458481.description: When a drug lord is fingered for murder, he hires three infamous hitmen to kill the witness. But can these three mavericks work together?

463190.title: El Ejecutor
463190.description: Le achacan a un tirador solitario el asesinato de un político, pero dos detectvies descubren un complot y luchan contra el poder detrás del crimen.

463208.title: Nameless Gangster
463208.description: When a corrupt official finds a large package of drugs, he joins forces with a dangerous mobster to take over the criminal underworld, one bullet at a time. Starring Choi Min-sik, leading man in iconic action film "Oldboy".

463719.title: Firepower
463719.description: A merc is hired by the FBI to track down a powerful recluse criminal. A woman is also trying to track him down for her own personal vendetta.

463727.title: Big Bad Mama II
463727.description: Wilma McClatchie and her sexy daughters return to a life of crime, and vow vengeance against the evil land baron who foreclosed on their home.

465009.title: Deadlier Than the Male
465009.description: British agent Bulldog Drummond is assigned to stop a master criminal who uses beautiful women to do his killings.

465391.title: Sinners and Saints
465391.description: Two New Orleans cops try to solve a string of murder cases that have ignited a gang war and realize there is an even more sinister force at play.

465936.title: Montana
465936.description: Betrayal and vengeance create a bond between a teenage boy who gets mentored by a commando in the dark arts of retribution against a drug mob.

466810.title: Love and Bullets
466810.description: A loner with a grudge against a mob boss jumps at the chance to get even when the FBI sends him to Switzerland to kidnap the gangster’s girlfriend.

466895.title: Nightstick
466895.description: New York City is going up in flames unless a maverick cop can stop a crew of terrorists holding the metropolis hostage with explosives.

466930.title: The Great Texas Dynamite Chase
466930.description: After busting out of the big house, a sexy jailbird picks up a feisty hitchhiker for a bank robbing binge that will soon become legendary.

468014.title: Dead Man Running
468014.description: An ex-con involves his best friend in a tangled mission, with only 24 hours to spare, to help raise the cash he owes to a deadly loan shark.

469532.title: Night Vision
469532.description: A maverick detective and his rookie partner hunt down a publicity-obsessed serial killer, who records his victims' deaths for posterity.

472543.title: Stoney
472543.description: Rivalry and crime collide in this heist adventure as crooks try to steal gold from a hidden vault beneath a commissioner’s pool in the Philippines.

473922.title: Moonshine County Express
473922.description: When a hillbilly moonshine-runner is murdered by a powerful rival, his three well-armed daughters take over the family business and swear vengeance.

476692.title: No Man's Land
476692.description: Everything changes for a Los Angeles rookie cop after he goes undercover to trap a wealthy auto buff who operates a hot-car ring.

477027.title: Down 'N Dirty
477027.description: When a cop loses his partner to a mysterious shooter, he teams up with a timid photographer to avenge the crime and expose a rat’s nest of corruption.

480254.title: Mafia
480254.description: Set in the 1970s, a crime boss and his crew leave bodies wherever they go while a detective and his partner will go to any lengths to bring them down.

485212.title: Street Dreams: Los Angeles
485212.description: An undercover cop with the LAPD stumbles upon a domestic terrorism case that could land him a position in the FBI’s counterintelligence division.

486394.title: The Heroin Busters
486394.description: A cold-blooded cop goes deep undercover to take down an international drug syndicate but when a hair-trigger Interpol agent joins the investigation, the case takes a deadly detour into sexual depravity and violence.

487715.title: Arizona Heat
487715.description: A sexist, old-school police officer teams up and clashes with a tough lesbian cop to hunt down a serial killer, who preys on law enforcement.

487961.title: Lockdown
487961.description: When a good cop is framed for murder and sent to prison, he must fight to survive and find a way to enforce his own brand of justice.

488308.title: On the Edge
488308.description: When a young basketball player entangles himself with drug dealers and ends up with a price on his head, he turns to an ex-cop and his pals for help.

489709.title: New York Cop
489709.description: An undercover cop from Japan infiltrates a crime syndicate in New York. But his growing bond with the gang's leader could threaten his life.

492792.title: The Collectors
492792.description: When a New Orleans mob boss sends two trusted hitmen men to New York City to collect overdue debts, alliances shift and chaos ensues.

493602.title: Vigilante
493602.description: When his wife and son are brutalized by street thugs, and a corrupt judge lets the criminals go free, a New York City factory worker vows revenge.

494842.title: Shottas
494842.description: Two young men from Jamaica climb to the top of the criminal world in Miami, with a constant presence of drugs, extortion, and deceit.

497833.title: Narco Valley
497833.description: An ex-kingpin resolved to a clean life following his release from prison is pulled back into crime, only to be deceived out of his rebuilt empire.

498191.title: Windfall
498191.description: Two thieves are caught in the act of robbing a casino vault, but instead of sending them to jail, the casino owner hires them as security consultants.

502471.title: Murder Gardens
502471.description: A teen leaves his foster father’s good home when his brother turns him on to drug dealing and local corruption, a world he now must survive to leave.

504644.title: Venice Underground
504644.description: When a turf war between two rival drug gangs kills a narcotics officer, a group of police cadets have 48 hours to solve the case or get suspended.

505797.title: Proxy War (Vol. 3)
505797.description: As Japan prepares to host the 1964 Olympic, two mobster gangs erupt into violence as complex and criminal double-crosses spiral out of control.

508060.title: Heaven's Burning
508060.description: After a failed bank robbery, a gang kidnaps a Japanese woman who’s trying to escape an arranged marriage, as the cops and her husband tail them.

508393.title: Blue Tiger
508393.description: A young mother’s grief outweighs danger after her little boy is killed by stray bullets from a Yakuza mob hit and she becomes dead set on revenge.

512395.title: Marie
512395.description: An ex-cop wants to live a quiet life until her husband is murdered, and she takes vengeance, unleashing a one-woman bloodbath on the mob.

513233.title: Underground President
513233.description: During a vicious gang war, a man seeks his identity and a link to his past, amidst intrigue, betrayal, and a secret that could unravel his whole life.

513566.title: The White Storm 2: Drug Lords
513566.description: After a 15-year personal rivalry, an underworld gang war erupts when a financier puts a price on the head of Hong Kong's most powerful drug dealer.

514067.title: The Last of the Finest
514067.description: An honorable LA cop and his crew discover a sinister plot and go rogue to battle an unholy alliance of smugglers, arms dealers, and government agents

515978.title: Shot
515978.description: Tasked with taking down a local drug kingpin, a detective duo enlists a low-level pusher and his girlfriend to go undercover to avoid prison.

516403.title: Rise Against the Fall
516403.description: 20 years after seeing his father assassinated at a political rally, a man becomes a mole in a brutal arms dealer’s inner circle to exact revenge.

517517.title: Among Thieves
517517.description: A group of thieves finds themselves stranded in a semi-trailer, after the only member capable of driving the getaway truck dies during their heist.

518383.title: Clockin' Green
518383.description: When a high-stakes bank robbery has two lifelong best friends running from the law, ultimate betrayal turns them into mortal enemies.

518981.title: 2 Dead 2 Kill
518981.description: An ex-narc stumbles upon clues to the location of a multi-million-dollar stash of stolen heroin and races against time and two drug lords to find it.

519173.title: Hollywood Cop
519173.description: In an intense action showdown, an undercover cop gets the better of a mob boss when he holds a little boy hostage for $6 million.

519516.title: Line of Descent
519516.description: In Delhi, three brothers in a warring crime family vie for power, while an undercover cop tries to bring them down, as he battles his own demons.

520101.title: Signal One
520101.description: A former LA cop hopes for a fresh start in Australia, where he’s drawn into the dark underworld of drugs and murder. Can he survive the mayhem?

521309.title: Vigilante Cop
521309.description: The true story of a San Antonio policeman who goes above and beyond the call of duty to stop his best friend, a fellow officer turned vigilante.

521808.title: She's Just a Shadow
521808.description: As a crime family engages in a vicious gang war, a serial killer terrorizes Tokyo and a dangerous love triangle ensues.

522193.title: Mean Johnny Barrows
522193.description: A black soldier kicked out of the army for striking an officer returns home to jail, abuse and crime until he’s hired as a hardcore mafia enforcer.

525261.title: Angel 2: Avenging Angel
525261.description: When the cop who saved and changed her life is slain, a former teen prostitute, now a law student, returns to the streets to face his mobster killers.

526186.title: La Dama de la Mafia (Doblado)
526186.description: Quedó huérfana veinte años atrás y ahora, desde el seno de la familia de la mafia que la adoptó, está decidida a vengar la muerte de sus padres.

526293.title: Pickings
526293.description: A mobster and his goons don't expect any resistance when they try to intimidate a bar owner, but the proprietor mercilessly turns the tables on them.

533892.title: Five Golden Dragons
533892.description: A cryptic note found on a dead man’s body tips a wealthy playboy to a gold-trafficking ring with a war between its kingpins and local, rival mobsters.

534224.title: South Beach
534224.description: The murder of a phone sex operator by a crazed killer leads her co-worker to seek the help of her ex-husband, a former NFL player-turned-detective.

535428.title: Freight
535428.description: A Russian gang enslaving and trafficking Eastern European women in the sex trade crosses the wrong businessman when they kidnap his daughter.

535536.title: Code of Thieves
535536.description: Making the mistake of robbing a powerful drug dealer, a group of friends are forced to rob a bank to make amends

541946.title: Majestic Thunderbolt (Español)
541946.description: No tomó nada bien que le robaran sus diamantes y transformándose en un arma mortal, él solo acaba con los yakuzas culpables uno por uno.

542960.title: By Quantum Physics: A Nightlife Venture
542960.description: Nightclub owner Lee Chan-Woo turns vigilante justice warrior when he decides to investigate a high-profile drug case involving a famous entertainer.

543775.title: We Still Steal the Old Way
543775.description: The Archer Gang are back and doing a daring heist in the heart of London...right up to the point when the armed police come crashing in.

545648.title: Outrage Coda
545648.description: This third installment of the Outrage trilogy finds former yakuza boss Otomo running enforcement in South Korea for a renowned and influential fixer.

548365.title: Queen Pin 2: The Restoration
548365.description: After the death of the original Queen Pin, Lil Miller and Killer have moved on to new business endeavors, but a tragedy brings them back in the game.

549529.title: The Butcher
549529.description: Merle Hench is a mob enforcer who has just escaped a deadly trap, and now he’s out for some good old-fashioned revenge against his former boss.

550347.title: Hollywood Vice Squad
550347.description: The ruthless underworld of mid-1980s Hollywood is exposed as a mother asks Vice Squad cops to help find her daughter, now a drug-addicted prostitute.

552676.title: El Coyote
552676.description: When an ex-mobster’s son is kidnapped, the mob descends on the Mexican border to take on the most powerful cartel in America.

553004.title: Dead or Alive
553004.description: A Yakuza member and a cop each wage their own war against the Japanese mafia. When they meet, their encounter will change the world.

560169.title: Soda Cracker
560169.description: A hardcore Chicago cop discovers an underground, deadly crime scheme between his fellow cops and dirty money after his partner is killed by a sniper.

561888.title: Five-O
561888.description: The story of two Detroit police officers who get in over their heads when they decide to take a crooked path involving a ruthless drug lord.

563804.title: 420 High Desert Way
563804.description: An undercover cop infiltrating a street drug ring is in a high-stakes race for survival after the kingpin starts to suspect a snitch in the ranks.

569444.title: Heat
569444.description: Set in Las Vegas, this is the tale of a tough bodyguard who has a soft spot for his friends, and takes their safety as his personal responsibility.

574351.title: Kill Kane
574351.description: After his wife and children are brutally murdered by a gang, a man decides that he must settle the score himself and sets out to avenge them.

576097.title: Dangerous Game
576097.description: To help his best friend pay off a gambling debt and avoid certain death, a footballer joins the dangerous ranks of Russian and Algerian gangsters.

576492.title: Highway 395
576492.description: The sheriff of a small community is challenged when he has to contend with drug runners, convicts and a serial killer all at the same time.

577807.title: The Henchman's War
577807.description: On assignment to kill a failed candidate, mob henchman Joe King also kills his wife, Miranda, a key component to why he lives a life of crime in obedient silence. Encompassed with regret and rage, Joe sets about killing those he blames for the traumatic events he and Miranda have endured.

580341.title: Street Savages
580341.description: A crime boss in a dangerous neighborhood does anything and everything in his power to make sure he maintains his power on the mean streets.

581996.title: Hit-and-Run Squad
581996.description: Internal Affair team has been disgraced while investigating a bribery case against the Police Commissioner and racer-turned-entrepreneur Jung Jae-chul. The second-in-command of the IA team, Lieutenant Eun Shi-yeon, is relegated to the Hit and Run Squad at Inchon PD. She meets Squad Captain Woo and constable Seo Min-jae, who has a natural instinct for cars and delinquent past. Eun also gets acquainted with Seo's family, who have met through car accidents. A hit and run case leads the squad to Jung as a prime suspect, Eun conducts a separate operation to acquire the black box in Jung's concept car. Jung, a reckless speed freak, chases Eun and it leads a tragic accident, costing someone's life. When Eun finds out the dirty deal behind her back, she cooperates with Seo to finally bring justice to Jung.

585812.title: On the Job
585812.description: The fact-based account of an overseas government scandal where high-ranking military personnel released prison inmates as contract killers on demand.

585840.title: The Thieves
585840.description: Five master thieves prep for the score of their lives as they each take their positions, from scaling walls to safecracking and brilliant disguises.

585846.title: The Gangster, the Cop, the Devil
585846.description: A crime boss with retribution on his mind after surviving a near-fatal attack by a serial killer convinces a detective to help catch the murderer.

589292.title: The Mask
589292.description: Jim Carrey’s superstar role as a kind and meek bank teller who gets super powers from a Nordic mask and becomes a totally s-s-s-smokin’ hero!

590502.title: Rook.
590502.description: After a pair of siblings and a small group attempt a gold heist and miserably fail, they most contend with hillbilly brothers ready to fight back.

592458.title: Narco Soldiers
592458.description: A Caribbean drug runner and his lover make their empire by instigating turf wars between foreign cartels – a decision that could kill them quickly.

594836.title: Mr. Narco
594836.description: En un mundo de drogas, dinero sucio y ansias de poder, la traición pagará su más alto precio. Mr. Narco tendrá que recorrer un largo camino lleno de violencia y muerte para consumar su venganza.

595031.title: Boss Moves
595031.description: When a woman coerces her husband into betraying his best friend, he becomes a sworn enemy.

595059.title: Leather Jackets
595059.description: Leather-jacketed Elwes and friends rip off and murder a Vietnamese mob bagman, whose associates vow vengeance.  A devastating human drama about love, friendship and the pain of growing up in a world gone wild. Leather Jackets explores the fragile relationship between three friends desperate to make sense of their lives before a brutal act of violence rips them apart.

598523.title: Calm Like A Bomb
598523.description: A man whose girlfriend was murdered takes revenge during the course of a single night. A spiral of shocking violence leaves no room for words. A man, his woman, three criminals and the distorted sounds of a city are the only reference.

600365.title: Snitch'd
600365.description: When the South Side Gang and the Cut Throat Mafia start a drug war at a local high school in Santa Ana, CA, detective McClure goes undercover to investigate the brutal murder of a young Latina student. The gang members are the key suspects but nobody is talking. And as McClure continues to dig for answers, it becomes clear that the two gangs are fighting for territory - and nobody is getting in their way.

601241.title: American Mobster: Miami Shakedown
601241.description: Nick Romano is a young Italian American fighting his own personal demons. He's got a chip on his shoulder and a lot to prove. Teamed with his crazy but always loyal partner Carlo, the two small time hoods are on the streets trying to hustle and make a living.

601995.title: The Alliance
601995.description: It’s been twenty years since four drug dealers have formed a peaceful pact, but after one member takes revenge on another, all hell breaks loose.

605700.title: The Grand Heist
605700.description: When corrupt officials corner the ice market, a gang of professionals from various fields goes on a mission to rob ice blocks from their storage unit.

605708.title: Troubleshooter
605708.description: A private detective who has been framed for murder has to obey a blackmailer’s orders that he clear his name within 24 hours – or else.

605720.title: Dope Game 2
605720.description: Gangsters come with badges as four rogue Oakland Task Force cops kill criminals and steal on the down low before coming up against a cold drug lord.

605722.title: Drug Lordz
605722.description: An Oakland mobster goes right back to building his drug empire when he gets out of jail, but a new kingpin and two detectives are closing in fast.

609478.title: Debt
609478.description: The girl-next-door in this crime tale is a ruthless debt collector for a crime syndicate and her next order is an old friend – will she quit or kill?

610418.title: Hitman's Hero
610418.description: After witnessing a murder as a child, Paul grows up to become a family man with a secret life as an assasin picking off marks in suburban Melbourne.

611015.title: Arrest Bulldog Drummond
611015.description: The former World War I British officer-turned-private investigator brings along his fiancee to help him catch dangerous spies with a stolen death ray.

611469.title: Project Gutenberg
611469.description: To take down a counterfeiting operation, led by a mastermind with a secret identity, Hong Kong police recruit a gang member to unmask the ringleader.

611656.title: Paydirt
611656.description: Five years after a DEA bust went wrong, a man recently released from prison teams up with his old gang to find a hidden bag of cash.

611693.title: Bulldog Drummond's Peril
611693.description: Captain Bulldog Drummond finds himself searching for a serial killer who has chosen his targets based on a priceless diamond in high demand.

612037.title: Honor Up
612037.description: In the wake of a devastating shootout, the lieutenant for a drug syndicate kingpin fights for his honor and to save his partners in crime.

612675.title: Sudden Fury
612675.description: An assassin turns the tables on his enemies when he gets betrayed by his employer, which sets off a chain reaction of violence among local gangsters.

612816.title: Bulldog Edition
612816.description: Competing newspaper men battle over business and for the affections of an intrepid reporter, but a local gangster complicates matters even further.

613755.title: Raising Wolves
613755.description: A drug kingpin’s master plan to extort money from a teen street gang backfires when they refuse to pay the ransom for his alleged kidnapping victim.

617054.title: Vendetta
617054.description: When his parents are slaughtered, a special ops interrogation officer must evade the police and his old unit in order to exact his gruesome revenge.

619646.title: Firestorm
619646.description: A humiliated police force foiled by a gang of daylight robbers tries to redeem itself by putting a hard boiled cop on the case with a lax moral code.

621694.title: Grimy
621694.description: An undercover cop who can get close to thugs who terrorize the streets with drugs and violence, is conflicted when assigned to his old neighborhood.

621979.title: The Criminal Mind
621979.description: On opposite sides of the law, a mafia boss and his district attorney younger brother go to war after one frames the other for a double murder.

622527.title: Cop's Enemy
622527.description: A man in a city of deadly cops and criminals goes undercover to help police bring down a gang — but betraying his girlfriend may be the last straw.

622622.title: Amateur Crook
622622.description: The daughter of a miner who foolishly loaned a priceless diamond to two loan sharks is mistaken as a thief as well by a confused artist.

625141.title: Assassin's Vow
625141.description: A drug lord in Miami sets up his resistant daughter in an arranged marriage to expand his international cartel while she fights hard for her freedom.

628105.title: You Only Live Once
628105.description: An investment banker gets caught up in a big money scheme and loses a million dollars. Now on the lam, he must survive a perilous night in Philly.

629153.title: The Pinch
629153.description: After a jaded mobster is given the short end of the stick one too many times, he takes matters into his own hands and kidnaps his boss.

630753.title: A Violent Prosecutor
630753.description: When a suspect he interrogated turns up dead, a volatile prosecutor is wrongly convicted of murder and enlists the aid of a conman to solve the crime.

631858.title: Nitro Rush
631858.description: A man escapes prison when he learns his son is in thrall to a female gangster and her crew. When his son won’t leave, the man joins in to protect him.

633211.title: Big Guns/No Way Out
633211.description: When a contract killer for the mob is brutally punished for trying to leave the game, he sets out on a revenge mission against his former bosses.

642292.title: Avenged
642292.description: An honest, but ambitious undercover cop risks his career, as well as his  life to settle a score with his corrupt superiors on the police force.

644045.title: L.A. Wars
644045.description: An undercover mission for loose cannon ex-cop Jake Quinn triggers a bloody war on the streets of L.A. between the mafia and a new rival drug gang.

648101.title: Gain the World
648101.description: The whole city comes after a small-time hood, who lands in big-time trouble, when he sells drugs to the wrong person, and a bounty is put on his head.

648179.title: Road
648179.description: A reformed criminal who went straight is thrust back into his old life to avenge the murder of his brother who was killed during a drug deal gone bad.

653890.title: Red Stone
653890.description: A hitman is tasked with hunting down the teenager who witnessed the murder of his older brother at the hands of a ruthless Southern crime lord.

654216.title: Stone
654216.description: When an undercover cop infiltrates an outlaw motorcycle gang, he'll take a full-throttle hell ride through sex, violence, and Down Under vengeance.

655773.title: Bad Day
655773.description: An undercover agent investigating London's South-Side mob discovers her daughter brutally murdered, leading her on a trail of vengeance.

657086.title: Sweet Karma
657086.description: In this gritty, violent, sexually charged film, a mute Russian girl infiltrates Toronto's underground sex trade to avenge the death of her sister.

660787.title: The Longest Run
660787.description: When a getaway driver is hired to move an endangered woman out of state, his menacing rival gives chase, as they settle old scores on the open road.

660843.title: Blazin'
660843.description: This inventive, underground version of Romeo and Juliet finds a street informant and his gang working to keep two lovers safe from assassins.

667139.title: Recognize
667139.description: By day, a clean-cut professional, Derrill Davis, has a dark side to his character, a brutal and feared street gangster that comes out at night.

673737.title: The Big Ugly
673737.description: Anglo-American relations turn sour when London mob bosses decide to invest in a West Virginia oil deal in hopes of laundering dirty money.

675590.title: In the Line of Duty: Street War
675590.description: After his partner is shot dead in a Brooklyn stairwell, a cop sets out to investigate and bring to justice the killer who took his friend.

675594.title: In the Line of Duty: The Price of Vengeance
675594.description: The friend of an assassinated prosecutor sets out to get revenge on Johnny Moore, the notorious gang leader who took his friend's life.

675596.title: In the Line of Duty: Mob Justice
675596.description: After slaying a federal drug agent, Costabile 'Gus' Farace finds himself wanted dead or alive by law enforcement and his mobster friends.

676277.title: The Con Artists
676277.description: An expert team of thieves that pull off a headline-grabbing heist are recruited for an operation against one of the continent’s top security systems.

681492.title: Mob War
681492.description: John Falcone, an unorthodox, violent, and sadistic mobster, finds himself at odds with Don Ricci, a mob boss who starts a war against him.

682048.title: Violent City
682048.description: A professional hit-man sets out to take revenge on the woman and the mob boss who used his mistress to set up a murder plot against him.

685920.title: Brawl in Cell Block 99
685920.description: After he's fired from his mechanic gig, a hot-tempered ex-boxer enters the drug-running game which lands him in the battleground of a brutal prison.

692972.title: Wrecker
692972.description: A construction worker-turned-vigilante faces off against a malevolent drug lord with plans to stage a citywide takeover using a sinister new drug.

694851.title: The Game Changer
694851.description: Two escaped prisoners come to have designs of their own after becoming the right-hand men of the head boss of Shanghai’s most powerful gang.

694873.title: Savage
694873.description: Buried by treacherous conditions at the top of Mt. Baekdu, a cop must brave extreme weather and a group of thieves until his transfer comes through.

696343.title: The Squeeze
696343.description: A retired safe cracker is lured back into the life for one last heist. After learning he's been double crossed, he plots his revenge.

697750.title: The Witness Protection Program
697750.description: Agent Diane Carter and her secret government agency offer safety and protection to those people placed in the Witness Protection Program.

698678.title: The Glove
698678.description: An ex-cop-turned-bounty hunter has his toughest assignment ever to capture a giant-sized ex-con donning body armor and steel-plated gauntlets.

698799.title: Chasing the Dragon II: Wild Wild Bunch
698799.description: An undercover agent infiltrates a notorious gang led by a billionaire kidnapping kingpin who’s terrorizing the city’s elite in 1990s Hong Kong.

699113.title: Til My Casket Drops
699113.description: Witnessing his mother’s murder as a kid turns Mayhem into a monster who comes to live by the gun, determined to get rich by any means necessary.

699324.title: Hindsight
699324.description: A young assassin gets sent to kill a retired mob boss, but things get complicated when they develop intense feelings for each other.

702579.title: Bring Him Back Dead
702579.description: After a heist goes wrong, a team of violent thieves gets sent to track down and eliminate the man who betrayed them and ran off with their loot.

705428.title: Yenni Thuniga
705428.description: After his fiancé is accidentally killed in a jewel heist gone wrong, a man seeks revenge on the gang responsible.

705474.title: Deep in It
705474.description: Kevin Hunter, a small-time thief who was just released from prison, is back home to take care of his young daughter and ailing mother.

705618.title: Federal Agents vs. Underworld, Inc.
705618.description: When an international crime boss steals an artifact that grants her the power to control minds, federal agents are dispatched to stop her evil plans.

707763.title: Mr. Mayfair: Shooting Paul – 4
707763.description: Hoping to put the past behind him and go legit, Max is persuaded by Paul to open a new Mister Mayfair club in the gangster haven of Portugal.

709233.title: Yakuza Wolf
709233.description: The son of a murder crime boss exacts his revenge by pitting two rival clans against each other and saving his sister from an elite trafficking ring.

709234.title: Yakuza Wolf 2
709234.description: Chiba exacts his revenge for the setup that sent him to prison by attacking Asao Uchida's lonely, clifftop mansion in a no-holds barred massacre.

712097.title: Justified Force
712097.description: A cop who comes out of retirement and his new partner will be forced to put their differences aside while investigating a dangerous drug operation.

712231.title: Messenger of Death
712231.description: Garret Smith travels to a sleepy Colorado town to investigate a brutal massacre and uncovers a sinister plot of greed and religious zealotry.

712443.title: Yo Soy La Patrona
712443.description: Tras un trágico accidente en el que muere su marido, Regina se hace cargo de su organización criminal y ahora es la nueva patrona del cartel.

714188.title: Number One with a Bullet
714188.description: After a blunder sends them to desk jobs, narcotics detectives Hazeltine and Berzak decide it’s time to take the law into their own hands.

0300008347.title: Crisis: Special Security Guard
0300008347.description: Five highly specialized agents that make up Tokyo's top-secret crime unit take on the cases that go above the paygrade of the regular police force.

0300009797.title: Hidden Identity
0300009797.description: Four elite police officers are recruited as part of a secret police unit, Investigation 5, that was formed to battle violent crimes.

0300007856.title: Pure
0300007856.description: Welcome to the streets of Buffalo, New York, where a clever hustler has just robbed one of the biggest gangsters, and must now team up with an enemy.

02944.title: Lives of Omission
02944.description: LEUNG SIU-TONG (Tse Tin Wah) joins the police force again to train up undercover cops for the Criminal Intelligence Bureau. He gets to know triad member SO SING-PAK (Bosco Wong) and becomes very good friends with him. PAK is not only smart guy also calculating. He agrees to work as TONG’s informer only because he sees TONG as a stepping-stone to the role of gang leader.

0300004776.title: The Protectors
0300004776.description: A crime-fighting team, made up of three international elites, make their way as a secret society to help the innocent and catch the guilty.

04200.title: Line Walker
04200.description: Undercover police agents lead double lives, until they discover that a mole has been inside the police force. Their world is about to crumble.

0300008840.title: The Professionals
0300008840.description: Welcome to Criminal Intelligence 5, a British anti-crime unit where two agents accept assignments to stop a series of vicious deviants.
